Oh, sorry, but I have a cute little daughter who's about to turn three—

121
00:06:06,300 --> 00:06:07,800
Telephone for you.

122
00:06:08,510 --> 00:06:10,670
Oh, thanks.

123
00:06:10,670 --> 00:06:12,810
Yes, hello, this is Hughes.

124
00:06:13,350 --> 00:06:14,590
Major?

125
00:06:15,580 --> 00:06:16,580
