create a Philosopher's Stone as well!

229
00:13:02,640 --> 00:13:04,220
Where is the manufacturing technique?!

230
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:09,560
What do you mean to do 
once you see it, Fullmetal Alchemist?

231
00:13:10,420 --> 00:13:14,210
The research is top secret 
and falls under my jurisdiction.

232
00:13:14,210 --> 00:13:16,630
I cannot permit you 
to see the materials.

233
00:13:17,160 --> 00:13:18,150
Let's go!

234
00:13:21,390 --> 00:13:24,950
L-Let go of me! No! No!

235
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:28,460
Please don't! Forgive me!

236
00:13:28,460 --> 00:13:30,450
I don't want to go back there!

237
00:13:30,450 --> 00:13:32,060
I don't want to go back!

238
00:13:32,900 --> 00:13:35,900
I've had enough of it! 
Please forgive me!

239
00:13:36,750 --> 00:13:37,580
I can't stand it!

240
00:13:38,420 --> 00:13:39,440
I can't stand anymore!

241
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:41,280
It's just like that other time...

242
00:13:52,180 --> 00:13:53,260
Brother!

243
00:13:55,620 --> 00:13:58,650
I may not have grown at all,

244
00:13:59,260 --> 00:14:02,190
