245
00:14:22,060 --> 00:14:23,670
Who's that?

246
00:14:23,970 --> 00:14:27,670
Iron Blood Alchemist, Basque Grand...

247
00:14:29,710 --> 00:14:31,430
Too bad for you!

248
00:14:31,430 --> 00:14:34,430
I now have this!

249
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:40,190
Stop!

250
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:54,700
<i>That's...</i>

251
00:14:54,700 --> 00:14:57,780
<i>That's the guy I saw three years ago 
in Central. I'm sure of it...</i>

252
00:14:58,410 --> 00:15:01,030
<i>Never mind that! This is bad!</i>

253
00:15:01,030 --> 00:15:03,170
<i>My instincts are telling me to run,</i>

254
00:15:03,580 --> 00:15:05,670
<i>but my legs won't move!</i>

255
